reviewText: The only place I could find these. My boys enjoyed watching these classics with me.
So convenient to have all of the faves in one, well priced bundle. If you love the House Party Franchise, then grab this for your collection.
I ordered this product and I'm in afghanistan and I still got it fast and on time this was geed

Its great to have these finally on DVD! they are classics! the first is still the best, but the second is good too.  The third is alright too.

Wonder what kid 'n' play up to now? Bilal did alright for himself!
